title: My Husband Is Really Feeling Himself
itunes:title: My Husband Is Really Feeling Himself
description:
Dear Steve and Shirley, I am a 28 year old wife and mother. My husband is 32. We’ve been together 10 years and got married 2 years ago. I don’t have any major complaints about my marriage, but my husband’s behavior is kind of strange lately. My husband and I met in college and we did what college couples do, we had sex every day or as much as we could. Now that I’m older and we have more responsibilities, I’m too tired to have sex everyday or as often as I’d like to...............
